 is\nallowed. This study may also find applications in macroscopic electrodynamics\nin the case of laser pumped medium or dissipative medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Dec 2013 07:44:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Mar 2014 01:20:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-02"}
