s\nachieved over a wide range of plasma conditions. It was demonstrated that\ntogether with long term reliability and modest access port requirements, LIDAR\ncan provide measurements of a quality similar to a conventional imaging Thomson\nScattering instrument.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Dec 2013 10:50:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-12"}
